DeathScythe stumbles back as the uppercut hits him in the chin, nearly 
causing him to drop his gun. He quickly puts away the gun, crouching for 
hand-to-hand combat.

"Yet is the keyword there," he says in his calm deadly whisper, a fist 
jabbing out at Hot Rod.
